title: Index of Factory Payrolls, New York State Factories for New York
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1914-1941 (2)--Original Data, 1935-1948. These Factories Are Representative Of New York State. Series Includes Both Office And Shop Workers. Source: The Industrial Bulletin, January 1942, P.9.

This NBER data series m08078a appears on the NBER website in Chapter 8 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter08.html.
